## Configuration Directives

You can use special configuration directives at the beginning of your script files using the `!` syntax:

```javascript
// Enable debug logging
!enableDebugging;

// Disable all logging
!disableLogging;

// Enable logging to file
!logToFile

// Hide the system tray icon
!hideTrayIcon
```